item.title: How do I give my self commands? like admin stuff
item.dc:creator: @m.dog311 m.dog311
item.description:
@m.dog311 wrote:

If you wana find the commands in your server here is a realy small tut
1)Open client.java
2)hold ctrl and hit f
3)in the little box that comes up type pure if your using pimpscape for testscape type startmine1
4)Those are just the first command in the LONG list of commands

Oh ya and if you see a small number in the line thats player rights

0=player
1=mod
2=admin
3=owner (rare though)
